OL,3,CThe mental health cycle
OL,5,FBut keeping a charity going is tough
OL,6,Fin this economic environment. As hard
OL,7,Fas it is, Terry, Zachary's dad, is
OL,8,Fplanning an equally tough physical
OL,9,Fchallenge. In June, he will cycle the
OL,10,Flength of Ireland over 24 hours,
OL,11,Fsomething which will test him mentally
OL,12,Fand physically.
OL,14,F"It's all about gravity, It pushes you
OL,15,Fdown. It hurts your legs, your arms,"
OL,16,Fhe tells me in this week's podcast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778198576
OL,3,CThe mental health cycle
OL,5,FBut Terry's passion for helping others
OL,6,Fwill help him push through. After all
OL,7,Fthis is his sixth cycle for the trust.
OL,8,FHe's already cycled over 20,000 miles
OL,9,Fand raised over #20,000.
OL,11,F"During every mile I cycle, I think of
OL,12,Fsomeone who is suffering. Someone who
OL,13,Fhas taken their own life and their
OL,14,Ffamilies, especially the young ones."
OL,16,FYasmin says that the trust not only
OL,17,Fhelps people but also advocates for
OL,18,Fimprovements to mental health
OL,19,Fcharities and tries to break down the
OL,20,Fstigma around talking about mental
OL,21,Fhealth.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
