OL,3,CThe mental health cycle
OL,5,F'The services are under pressure.
OL,6,FPeople are being put on waiting lists
OL,7,Fbut I never heard of anyone's mental
OL,8,Fhealth improving while being on a
OL,9,Fwaiting list....I think the trusts
OL,10,Fcould communicate much better with
OL,11,Fthose looking for help. Communication
OL,12,Fis key.'
OL,14,FBut Terry is clear on what he believes
OL,15,Fanyone struggling with mental health
OL,16,Fshould do...talk.
OL,18,F"Just tell someone, anyone." A
OL,19,Fteacher, a doctor, a friend, an aunt,
OL,20,Fa brother, anyone. Just open up
OL,21,Fgradually. Just talk.'
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
